	nRescued: Two Class IV girls who had fled home for fear of failing in an exam were rescued by police and handed over to their parents on Thursday. Cops found the duo roaming around in Ekbalpore Lane.        
	nDead: Amiya Poddar, 56, died when the verandah of a two-storeyed building in Beleghata collapsed around 7.30am on Thursday. He was declared brought dead at NRS hospital.                                                                                                                                                          
